{"tid":2457620,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李麗蕊被梁思浩指價值觀不同 拒合作斷聯絡","createTime":"2021-03-22T19:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T05:52:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2397ad8cbc552e47f5fbd2cdfbcc07f48dab31c5","tid":2457620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T19:45:10.000Z","msg":"李麗蕊坦言斷絕合作後，雙方已再沒有聯絡，她說：「知佢搵咗另一啲人繼續做節目，祝福佢，我冇所謂，啱就做，唔啱就唔做。」會否當梁思浩仍是朋友？李麗蕊說：「我會話係，做嘢啫！唔會因為呢啲嘢影響到，有啲啲唔開心，識咗咁耐友誼就係咁奇怪，因為好小嘅事，合則來不合則散，今日我已經放低咗，唔會再介意。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210322/JUDHJU6AMNBKFISOXMKIMWHETE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210322%2FJUDHJU6AMNBKFISOXMKIMWHETE%2F&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=bbccf364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210322%2FJUDHJU6AMNBKFISOXMKIMWHETE%2F&h=321278e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210322/JUDHJU6AMNBKFISOXMKIMWHETE/</a>"},{"pid":"5b2d2bfe4a16d25e9619f8bacd5b3411f2247102","tid":2457620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T23:56:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ff43655d13b5c11b209dc189be9e4dcd01cc1e3b","tid":2457620,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T00:32:53.000Z","msg":"Noted"},{"pid":"8759aa3e65a5de21caf076ac024c8f0f5973dc6f","tid":2457620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T05:52:31.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}